name: Postcard from my home
description:
We travel to know, we travel to come back.
We belong to the places that made us experiment our life. 
We owe to people that love us and the ones that are waiting for us to continue sharing presence. 
Would I have enjoyed my flight so much without the certainty that I could come back whenever I wanted?

-

Viajamos para conocer, viajamos para volver.
Somos de los lugares que nos han hecho experimentar la vida, nos debemos a las personas que nos quieren y esperan para seguir compartiendo la presencia.
¿Hubiese disfrutado tanto de mí vuelo sin la certeza de que podía volver cuando quisiera?
